     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet vs-senologie-diagnose</b></p><a name=\"vs-senologie-diagnose\"> </a><a name=\"hcvs-senologie-diagnose\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://www.snomed.org/\"><code>http://snomed.info/sct</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated. No matching Code System found\"> version Not Stated (use latest from terminology server)</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/254837009\">254837009</a></td><td>Malignant neoplasm of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/109889007\">109889007</a></td><td>Ductal carcinoma in situ of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/254845004\">254845004</a></td><td>Fibroadenoma of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/27431007\">27431007</a></td><td>Fibrocystic disease of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/399123008\">399123008</a></td><td>Benign retention cyst of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/449837001\">449837001</a></td><td>Complex cyst of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/83620003\">83620003</a></td><td>Non-puerperal mastitis</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/1287638006\">1287638006</a></td><td>Puerperal mastitis</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/16698000\">16698000</a></td><td>Non-puerperal breast abscess</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/10745131000119107\">10745131000119107</a></td><td>Abscess of breast associated with lactation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/237444008\">237444008</a></td><td>Granulomatous mastitis</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/269497004\">269497004</a></td><td>Neoplasm of uncertain behavior of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/53430007\">53430007</a></td><td>Mastalgia</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/237473006\">237473006</a></td><td>Ruptured breast implant</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/4754008\">4754008</a></td><td>Gynecomastia</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/718220008\">718220008</a></td><td>At high risk for hereditary breast and ovarian cancer syndrome</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/1306515008\">1306515008</a></td><td>Recurrent primary malignant neoplasm of breast</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/43336006\">43336006</a></td><td>Gigantomastia</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/290113009\">290113009</a></td><td>Bloody nipple discharge</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://snomed.info/id/237474000\">237474000</a></td><td>Contracture of breast following insertion of breast implant</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal.html\"><code>https://www.senologie.org/fhir/CodeSystem/cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?0.1.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal.html#cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal-bz-diagnose-sonstiges\">bz-diagnose-sonstiges</a></td><td>Sonstiges</td><td>Sonstige Diagnose, nicht anderweitig klassifiziert</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal.html#cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal-bz-mamillensekretion-nicht-blutig\">bz-mamillensekretion-nicht-blutig</a></td><td>Nicht blutige Mamillensekretion</td><td>Sekretion aus der Brustwarze, nicht blutig (SNOMED 54302000 deckt nur 'Discharge from nipple' ohne Spezifizierung)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal.html#cs-senologie-diagnose-lokal-bz-anisomastie\">bz-anisomastie</a></td><td>Anisomastie</td><td>Asymmetrie der Brüste (kein exaktes SNOMED-Äquivalent als Diagnose)</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
